Once the request is received by the server, it gets processed very fast and the response is near instant.

> I would like to know about the error on other side? Can you please get me information.

It was caused by user input being casted to another data type and this regular expression in the numericality validation: https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/activemodel/lib/active_model/validations/numericality.rb#L70.
